Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:11.28,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:15.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:22.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:26.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:30.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:33.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:36.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:40.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:44.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:48.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:50.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:54.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:59.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:15.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:18.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,155.389)}Ambassador Hell!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,710.389)}His Fearsome True Form?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Release the water from the dam!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It would wipe the\Ncity downstream...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino City... off the map!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.97,0:02:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All two million people who use this\Nlake as water supply are going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Rattlander, have filled\Nthe lake with my deadly venom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Venom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Open the sluice gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker monster, Rattlander...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How did you learn of my plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A member of Shocker informed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a traitor in Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That cannot be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I hardly believed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seems the tip was correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But who could have\Nleaked the information?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you already know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I have always followed\Nyour orders loyally!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rattlander reported that\Nthere is a traitor in Shocker
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,who leaked our plan\Nto the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And you think that was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation: Poisoned Reservoirs\Nwas a top Shocker secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The only ones who knew\Nabout it were you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell... you are the traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep him in a cell until his execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what I said was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pigeon we haven't seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Registry number 0001.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have that number.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:59.28,Italics,,0,0,0,,My dearest Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the voice of Shocker's leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:07.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,The execution of your mortal\Nenemy, commander-in-chief
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:09.96,Italics,,0,0,0,,of Shocker's Japan branch, Ambassador Hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:15.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,has been scheduled for September 30th\Nat 4:00 PM in the 8th warehouse at Harumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:19.38,Italics,,0,0,0,,You are hereby invited to attend,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:22.33,Italics,,0,0,0,,to serve as a witness to\NAmbassador Hell's execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:25.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,For the time of your attendance,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:29.16,Italics,,0,0,0,,Shocker pledges not to lay a hand upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell's being executed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be fools to take\NShocker at their word!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It might indeed be a trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't let them kill Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,After everything he's\Nput us through? He's a villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should we object\Nif they turn on their own?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell might've been the one who\Nleaked the plan about the reservoir last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's entirely possible that Ambassador Hell\Ncould have turned on them for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You must wear a blindfold\Nfrom this point onward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you and I have\Na truce today, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Don't be rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We will now commence the execution
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of the former Shocker\Ncommander, Ambassador Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Traitorous Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a worthy foe for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,yet you came here to serve\Nas my witness today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let my last words be an\Nexpression of gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I consider it an honor to\Nserve as your witness as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Commence the execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.56,0:09:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Remain calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Retrieve Hongo and Ambassador Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Ambassador Hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He may be a traitor to Shocker,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but I still need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just let you kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's just against combatants,\Nhe'll be by soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's just combatants, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... You think Rattlander might show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Our leader created a mystery\Nmonster without my knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A mystery monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the reason I betrayed Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ganikomoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Shocker monster, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Think that, if you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Our last battle taught me\Nall I need to know about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:59.38,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You were their commander-in-chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you not know\NGanikomoru's true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive my ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is world domination worth,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,if your leader doesn't trust you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've grown sick of Shocker's methods!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I leaked Rattlander's\Npoisoned reservoir plot to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,About that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about that unknown monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but we need to take care\Nof Rattlander first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Rattlander's next target?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He spent all of his venom\Nin the reservoir last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably gone to restock his venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Rattlander is a cyborg based off\Nof that desert snake, the rattlesnake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He would live in the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anywhere like\Na desert in the area?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamamatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You should stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to learn more about Shocker, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave myself in your hands, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, we'd rather not\Nhave you in our hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, we're heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you whispering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi pulled his neck\Nout of the guillotine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a Shocker commander anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But Colonel Zol was\Nactually Wolf Man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And Doctor Shinigami was\Nsecretly Squidevil, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker commanders-in-chief\Nhave always been cyborgs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ambassador Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The pigeons are afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a rat or a cat is stalking them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The animal pigeons fear most\Nis the sound of the snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just any snake,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but a rattlesnake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The women were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All Shocker commanders are cyborgs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the true form of Shocker's\Ngreatest commander-in-chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rattlander!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the execution was all an act?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To deceive your enemies,\Nyou must deceive your allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And even Hongo and Taki\Nnow trust me implicitly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so big. I wouldn't even\Nknow where to start...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with the center\Nof the dunes, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yuri!\N- Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell...\Nyou were never a traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Shocker's high commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never betray Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a dirty trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cry and suffer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the real execution will begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you gone mad, Hongo Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you laughing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think we\Ncame to these dunes blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We prepared for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Disperse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally time to end you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the power of Rattlander!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell's true form...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.19,0:20:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:10.42,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Jump! Dive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:12.16,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Slam into them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:14.84,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Give it all you've got! Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:19.98,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Hit them with the force of a storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:23.57,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:27.63,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:31.58,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:46.67,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,He came here in a roar...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:48.87,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:50.73,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of lamentation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:54.36,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,who brings evil plots to light?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:56.52,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.36,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.34,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Fly! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:01.70,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Get the dynamo humming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:04.24,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Full charge! Full charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:09.87,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Hit them with an engine's roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:13.66,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:17.68,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:21.60,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I will return from the\Ndead and destroy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.56,0:22:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker forces... are eternal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.57,0:22:16.12,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:19.37,Italics,,0,0,0,,Shocker's Japan Branch is hereby disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:22.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,I can now create a more\Nfearsome organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:24.78,Italics,,0,0,0,,We shall meet again, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A more fearsome organization, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally time for\Nus to show ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... I shall destroy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.34,0:23:00.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell was secretly\Nthe Shocker cyborg Rattlander.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.34,0:23:04.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the monster Ganikomoru\Nwas about to lift his veil of mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:08.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What is the new organization\Nthat will replace Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:10.97,Cont,,0,60,150,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:13.85,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(290.175,252.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.50,0:23:18.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Geldam has joined Shocker\Nto create Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:20.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let us celebrate the merger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:23.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker will surely conquer Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.68,0:23:26.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and destroy the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.12,0:23:27.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Go, General Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.50,0:23:30.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Go, Ganikomoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:31.03,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,210.389)}Gel Shocker's Debut!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:31.03,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs115\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,690.389)}The Last Day of Kamen Rider!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:50.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground\Nwith a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:57.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.96,0:24:01.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning\Nwith a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.71,0:24:05.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies\Nwith a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.53,0:24:09.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:13.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell!!\NHis Fearsome True Form?
Comment: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker's Debut!\NThe Last Day of Kamen Rider!!